{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Grid Column","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Grid_Column","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>网格列</strong>是<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">Grid 布局</a>中的垂直轨道，即两个垂直网格线之间的空间。它通过属性 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a> 或者简写属性 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid\"><code>grid</code></a>，<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code></a> 定义。</p>\n<p>另外，当项目被放置到显示网格中创建的列外面时，可以在隐式网格中创建网格列。默认情况这些列自动调整大小，也可以使用 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code></a> 属性指定其大小。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout\">Grid 布局</a>中使用对齐方式时，网格列沿着纵轴运行。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性参考","title":"属性参考","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template-columns\"><code>grid-template-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-auto-columns\"><code>grid-auto-columns</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid\"><code>grid</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/grid-template\"><code>grid-template</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"扩展阅读","title":"扩展阅读","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>CSS Grid Layout Guide: <em><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout/Basic_Concepts_of_Grid_Layout\">Basic concepts of grid layout</a></em></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"网格列是Grid 布局中的垂直轨道，即两个垂直网格线之间的空间。它通过属性 grid-template-columns 或者简写属性 grid，grid-template 定义。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Grid Column","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Grid Column","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":